        blog for updates on writing progress, technology research, and travel inspiration.
      </p>
      <div class="book-actions">
        <a class="button" href="/blog">Visit the blog</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/author">About the author</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
